    "How can the machine help you learn how to exercise your grammatical capacities to mean for yourself?",
    "How can it suggest a range of alternative interpretations to support you in forming your own interpretation of the text?",
    "When properly calibrated for educational application, Generative AI has the potential do all of these things.",
    "We want to call this humancomputer relation \"cyber-social literacy learning.",
    "\"As an aside-and we expand on this argument elsewhere (Cope and Kalantzis 2024c)-we think that \"artificial intelligence\" is an unhelpful idea."
